<paragraph blockId="82.[151,1437,150,861]" pageId="82" pageNumber="83">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,384,150,176]" pageId="82" pageNumber="83">Material examined.</emphasis>
Ten specimens, including the 
<typeStatus box="[722,831,150,176]" pageId="82" pageNumber="83">holotypes</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Shinohara" authorityYear="1988" box="[867,1018,151,176]" class="Insecta" family="Pamphiliidae" genus="Pamphilius" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="82" pageNumber="83" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ussuriensis">
<emphasis box="[867,1018,151,176]" italics="true" pageId="82" pageNumber="83">P. ussuriensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Shinohara" authorityYear="1988" box="[1072,1198,151,176]" class="Insecta" family="Pamphiliidae" genus="Pamphilius" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="82" pageNumber="83" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="zinovjevi">
<emphasis box="[1072,1198,151,176]" italics="true" pageId="82" pageNumber="83">P. zinovjevi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, all from the Russian Far East and South Korea (
<bibRefCitation author="Shinohara, A." box="[467,664,186,212]" pageId="82" pageNumber="83" pagination="307 - 320" refId="ref76348" refString="Shinohara, A. (1988 a) The group of Pamphilius sylvaticus (Hymenoptera, Pamphiliidae): Five new species and additional records from the Far East. Kontyu, Tokyo, 56, 307 - 320." type="journal article" year="1988">
Shinohara 1988 
<bibRefCitation author="Shinohara, A." box="[651,664,186,212]" pageId="82" pageNumber="83" pagination="99 - 116" refId="ref76721" refString="Shinohara, A. (2001) The group of Pamphilius sylvaticus (Hymenoptera, Pamphiliidae): Two new species, new collection records, and a key to Palearctic species. Japanese Journal of Systematic Entomology, 7, 99 - 116." type="journal article" year="2001">a</bibRefCitation>
</bibRefCitation>
, 2001; present work). 
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="82" pageNumber="83">
New collection data: 
<collectingCountry box="[1184,1291,186,212]" name="Russia" pageId="82" pageNumber="83">RUSSIA</collectingCountry>
: 
<collectingRegion country="Russia" name="Primorskiy" pageId="82" pageNumber="83">Primorskij Kraj</collectingRegion>
</emphasis>
: 
